  "detailed_description": "<strong>ASTRO ACE is a retro-style addictive arcade space shooter.</strong><br>From the distant universe, an evil alien fleet is invading the solar system. <br>You will have to ride a powerful spaceship and fight against endless waves of enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3153d2f097b09bf57325093ea417046e.webp?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=45 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• You have to battle an endless wave of enemies in a universe surrounded by radiation walls. You can use the boost, brake, and left and right turns to avoid attacking enemies or aim behind them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• There are more than 10 types of weapons: cannon, laser, plasma, and missile, etc. Eliminate enemies with your own way. Don't forget to replenish your ammo and energy to destroy more enemy ships and survive longer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• When you shoot down 5 Elite ships of the enemy, you can get powerful Wingman support for 15 seconds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• Make your ship more powerful through various power-ups and prepare for extreme boss battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/cdb118d570aa8d7de8811a0e161e004e.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/cdb118d570aa8d7de8811a0e161e004e.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/cdb118d570aa8d7de8811a0e161e004e.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• Level up to use the weapon you want from the start or unlock new ships and equipment for your support.<br><br>• Get a higher score than the other aces and rank at the top of the leaderboard.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/0fb88e10f07ab015ed1aeff14af260c0.webp?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=45 /></span><br><br>• Endless waves of a variety of enemies.<br><br>• Challenging boss stage battles.<br><br>• 10 Playable spaceships.<br><br>• 14 unique primary weapons.<br><br>• 7 powerful secondary weapons.<br><br>• 3 levels power-ups of range, damage, etc.<br><br>• Unlockable ships, paint jobs, and support equipment.<br><br>• Steam leaderboards, Steam cloud support, and Achievements.<br><br>• Keyboard, Gamepad Support.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>ASTRO ACE is a retro-style addictive arcade space shooter.</strong><br>From the distant universe, an evil alien fleet is invading the solar system. <br>You will have to ride a powerful spaceship and fight against endless waves of enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3153d2f097b09bf57325093ea417046e.webp?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=45 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/c5b0bcc7a9f4bf6c129dfecb86c9ec47.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• You have to battle an endless wave of enemies in a universe surrounded by radiation walls. You can use the boost, brake, and left and right turns to avoid attacking enemies or aim behind them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/36d6ea851c5beab77ae24a8ca0e8f7a8.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• There are more than 10 types of weapons: cannon, laser, plasma, and missile, etc. Eliminate enemies with your own way. Don't forget to replenish your ammo and energy to destroy more enemy ships and survive longer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/3d17d3956d99a4c5701f7bff98dba834.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• When you shoot down 5 Elite ships of the enemy, you can get powerful Wingman support for 15 seconds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.webm?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/666727f94374db90d36854efb50a7000.mp4?t=1648537681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>• Make your ship more powerful through various power-ups and prepare for extreme boss battles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/cdb118d570aa8d7de8811a0e161e004e.poster.avif?t=1648537681\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444770/extras/cdb118d570aa8